<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f2ede4; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
.container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 32px; }
.header { color: #3a8a1e; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.btn { display: inline-block; background: #3a8a1e; color: #fff !important; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; margin: 16px 0; }
.footer { color: #7a7a72; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 32px; border-top: 1px solid #dedad2; padding-top: 16px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<div class="header">🐾 Compawgnon</div>
{% block content %}{% endblock %}
<div class="footer">© 2026 Compawgnon — Plateforme d'achat et d'adoption d'animaux<br>Si vous n'êtes pas à l'origine de cette action, ignorez cet email.</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
